To gather slice:

  1. copy lines [7,13] to your .usr file
  2. change FB_FORCE to 1
  3. copy lines [114,136] to userchk file. Also make sure parameter(nstat=25) precedes this block.
  4. copy lines [371,466] to somewhere in your userchk subroutine
  
To go back to old mode:

  1. change INTP_SLICE to 0
